direction: right

*.style.border-radius: 8
*.style.font-size: 13
*.style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
*.style.stroke: "#333333"

# --- Entry ---

entry: |md
  **/rfe-creator.update-deps**

  Force update vendored
  dependencies
| {style.fill: "#f5f5f5"; style.stroke: "#333333"; style.stroke-width: 2}

# --- Step 1: Update assess-rfe ---

clean-assess: |md
  **Clean assess-rfe**

  `rm -rf`
  `.context/assess-rfe`
  `.claude/skills/assess-rfe`
  `.claude/skills/export-rubric`
| {style.fill: "#fde8e8"; style.stroke: "#333333"; style.stroke-width: 2}

bootstrap-assess: |md
  **Bootstrap assess-rfe**

  `bootstrap-assess-rfe.sh`
  Clone / pull assess-rfe repo
  Copy skills + agents
  Patch PLUGIN_ROOT
  Export rubric
| {style.fill: "#e8e8e8"; style.stroke: "#333333"; style.stroke-width: 2}

# --- Step 2: Update architecture context ---

clean-arch: |md
  **Clean arch context**

  `rm -rf`
  `.context/architecture-context`
| {style.fill: "#fde8e8"; style.stroke: "#333333"; style.stroke-width: 2}

fetch-arch: |md
  **Fetch arch context**

  `fetch-architecture-context.sh`
  Detect latest RHOAI version
  Sparse checkout from
  architecture-context repo
| {style.fill: "#e8e8e8"; style.stroke: "#333333"; style.stroke-width: 2}

# --- Step 3: Report ---

report: |md
  **Report**

  List updated deps
  and fetched versions
| {style.fill: "#d1fae5"; style.stroke: "#333333"; style.stroke-width: 2}

# --- External ---

assess-rfe-repo: |md
  **n1hility/assess-rfe**
  _(GitHub)_
| {style.fill: "#f5f5f5"; style.stroke: "#333333"; style.stroke-width: 2; style.stroke-dash: 3}

arch-repo: |md
  **opendatahub-io/**
  **architecture-context**
  _(GitHub)_
| {style.fill: "#f5f5f5"; style.stroke: "#333333"; style.stroke-width: 2; style.stroke-dash: 3}

# --- Edges ---

entry -> clean-assess: "Step 1"
clean-assess -> bootstrap-assess
bootstrap-assess -> clean-arch: "Step 2"
clean-arch -> fetch-arch
fetch-arch -> report: "Step 3"

# External edges
bootstrap-assess -> assess-rfe-repo: "git clone/pull" {style.stroke-dash: 3}
fetch-arch -> arch-repo: "sparse checkout" {style.stroke-dash: 3}
